Comment: 2,0:22:25.37,0:22:27.91,OP-CH,,0,0,60,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}Please remember
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.24,0:22:33.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\c&H6561D9&\shad3}一次就好 希望你能许愿 愿奇迹降临
